spec_data.Name: perl-Encode-DoubleEncodedUTF8
spec_data.Description:
Encode::DoubleEncodedUTF8 adds a new encoding utf-8-de and fixes
double encoded utf-8 bytes found in the original bytes to the correct
Unicode entity.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:25:17 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Fix double encoded UTF-8 bytes to the correct one
